app_description: Italian Keyboard Italian Keyboard is the best app for Italian writing. Italian keyboard app will allow you to write message story facebook posts blogs Emails in Italian language. you will find eye catchy and userfriendly Italian keyboard to write Italian language. Italian keyboard has easiest keypad to write Italian alphabets letters and words. you just type Italian words you can find suggestions of that Italian words automatically in this application. The most exciting feature of this application is you can translate Italian word to any other language like English Marathi Italian Italian and all other indian languages as well as all international languages like French Spanish Greek Turkish Sweedish etc.... Features : you can easily change English to Italian and Italian to English keypad using Italian Keyboard application. you can translate Italian words into any other Indian and International languages. You can edit the text and also change the color of the font. It s also provide all the emoji icons Italian keyboard has special characters icons and numeric so that user can easily write any Italian words very esay and effective manner. its free and easy to use.
